graph LR
    %% Entities
    Finder[Finder Student]
    Loser[Loser Student]
    Admin[Admin Desk Staff]

    %% Data Store
    DB(Lemon MVP Data Store: JSON File)

    %% Processes
    P1[1.0 Submit Item Report]
    P2[2.0 Index & Match Records]
    P3[3.0 Query & Search Index]
    P4[4.0 Manage Claim Verification]

    %% Flow Streams
    Finder -->|Found Item Details Form| P1
    P1 -->|Insert New Record Data| DB
    
    DB -->|Read Unresolved Records| P2
    P2 -->|Trigger Potential Match Notification| Loser
    
    Loser -->|Search Keywords / Filters| P3
    P3 -->|Query Matching Records| DB
    DB -->|Display Search Results / Item Details| P3
    P3 -->|View Item Information| Loser

    Admin -->|Verification & Claims Updates| P4
    P4 -->|Update Status to Claimed/Returned| DB
